sibes_merge This function merges the tibbels samples and biota on samples data frame using left_join().

Source: R/sibes_merge.R
sibes_merge.Rd

sibes_merge This function merges the tibbels samples and biota on samples data frame using left_join().

sibes_merge(Inputdata)

Arguments

Inputdata

List containing the tibbles 'biota' and 'samples'.

Value

A merged tibble of samples and biota that also contains empty stations.

Examples

data_list <- get('SIBES_dataset')
sibes_merge(Inputdata = data_list)
